Others: Tunisia earned a goalless draw away to Namibia.
Senegal kept up their unbeaten start to 2026 World Cup qualification with a 1-0 win away at Mauritania.
There was a lengthy delay in completing the match after frustrated home fans threw objects towards the pitch in the second half and proceedings were halted.
Namibia had the ball in the net after 14 minutes but it was disallowed due to a foul on the goalkeeper, though replays suggested minimal contact.
